style is slow ballads for the most part. one or two of the songs got alot of airplay on latin radio, for example "si la ves". no comment about the quality of the mp3s as I've spotted an EAC rip on a private tracker ;-)
I have to sing this song for spanish class so it helps to have it at home, thanks!
